name: iPhone 5/5S Light Purple Gloss Carbon Fiber TPU Case
description:
•Keep your Apple iPhone 5 safe and protected in style with dual-layered protective accessory case

•Slip your cell phone in to add a splash of color and deliver instant all-around protection from scratches

•Constructed from smooth, treated rubber that resists dirt and stains

•Ridged design for better grip

•Unique design allows easy access to all buttons, controls and ports without having to remove the skin

•TPU, also known as thermoplastic polyurethane, is more cut and tear resistant than rubber. It is abrasion resistance, and has a high degree of transparency. Compared to silicone skins, this skin is stiffer to the touch, but remains flexible

•Shock absorbent, shatterproof, and anti-scratch material

•Material: TPU Rubber

•Gloss carbon fiber vinyl installed on the case

•Auto grade carbon fiber used, strong and durable material

name: iPhone 4/4S Red Gloss Carbon Fiber Hard Plastic Case
description:
•Ultra thin, Slim fit, does not make your Phone look bulky.

•This compact product provides excellent protection for your iPhone 4/4S and keeps your iPhone 4/4S with thin shape.

•This brand new, high quality case is made of durable clear plastic material that resists dirt, dusts to extend the life of your iPhone 4/4S.

•Unique design allows easy access to all buttons, controls and ports without having to remove the case.

•Material: Hard plastic

•Gloss carbon fiber vinyl installed on the case

•Auto grade carbon fiber used, strong and durable material
